OL,6,FFour teenagers who brutally stabbed a
OL,7,F16-year-old schoolboy to death in a
OL,8,Fhorrific daytime machete attack have
OL,9,Fbeen convicted of murder.
OL,11,FJoseph Riches was stabbed in Coventry
OL,12,FStreet, , on Saturday 15 July and was
OL,13,Fdriven to Rowley Regis, where he was
OL,14,Fpronounced dead at the scene.JOne of
OL,15,Fthe attackers viciously plunged a
OL,16,Fmachete into his chest before fleeing
OL,17,Fthe scene, Coventry Crown Court heard.
