OL,6,FJoseph scrambled into a car driven by
OL,7,Fhis friends but bled to death in the
OL,8,Fvehicle. His body was discovered in
OL,9,Fthe car when it was dumped four miles
OL,10,Faway from the scene of the killing.
OL,12,FDray Simmonds and Joshua Edgington,
OL,13,Fboth 20, and two 16-year-olds, who
OL,14,Fcannot be named for legal reasons,
OL,15,Fwere found guilty of murder today (13
OL,16,FFebruary).
OL,18,FThe trial heard Simmonds, who was 19
OL,19,Fat the time, inflicted the fatal blow.
OL,20,FThe other three defendants were
OL,21,Fconvicted on a joint enterprise basis.
