OL,6,FJoseph, from Bartley Green,
OL,7,FBirmingham, was in Stourbridge town
OL,8,Fcentre with friends on the day of his
OL,9,Fmurder, the court heard, when he
OL,10,Fspotted another group of teenagers and
OL,11,Fran up to them at the bottom of High
OL,12,FStreet.
