OL,6,FJoseph attacked two of them with a
OL,7,Fscrewdriver before attempting to get
OL,8,Finto a car with his friends which had
OL,9,Fpulled up alongside him, jurors were
OL,10,Ftold.JBut the teenager struggled to
OL,11,Fget into the car and ran off along
OL,12,FCoventry Street as he was chased.
OL,13,FJoseph was then attacked himself,
OL,14,Fsuffering a fatal blow to the chest.
OL,15,FHe managed to get to his feet and got
OL,16,Finto the car with his friends who had
OL,17,Fdriven up Coventry Street to meet him.
OL,18,FBut he was later discovered dead in
OL,19,Fthe car which had been abandoned four
OL,20,Fmiles away on Orchard Close, Rowley
OL,21,FRegis.JThe machete was found by a
OL,22,Fmember of the public under a fire
OL,23,Fescape on High Street, Stourbridge.
OL,24,FSimmonds was arrested the next day,
OL,25,Fwhile his accomplices were detained
OL,26,Flater that evening after turning up at
